WEBVTT

00:01.317 --> 00:02.660
(EXPLOSION, GLASS SHATTERS)

00:02.661 --> 00:03.452
Aah!

00:04.946 --> 00:06.146
Wait, you think Damien
has something to do

00:06.147 --> 00:07.846
with Kelly's death, don't you?

00:07.846 --> 00:10.096
He needs our help, not our suspicion.

00:10.097 --> 00:11.645
_

00:11.646 --> 00:13.918
_

00:13.919 --> 00:16.164
_

00:16.165 --> 00:17.320
(WHISPERS) How do you
know we can trust her?

00:17.321 --> 00:19.170
She's a nun. I think she
can make sense of things.

00:19.171 --> 00:22.106
Simone says you think there's
another person involved?

00:22.107 --> 00:24.341
Yeah. Uh, her name's Veronica.

00:24.342 --> 00:26.774
Listen to me, Amani.
It's not what you think.

00:26.775 --> 00:28.822
You used me to get to my friend.

00:28.823 --> 00:31.725
- It's not me. It's my mother.
- Stay the hell away from him.

00:32.026 --> 00:33.799
Ran into an old buddy of
yours the other night.

00:33.800 --> 00:36.262
- Is that Cray Marquand?
- Somebody cut out his tongue.

00:36.263 --> 00:39.233
- You failed him, Charles.
- Guard, let me out of here!

00:39.234 --> 00:41.033
You are nothing!

00:41.034 --> 00:42.868
Uhh! Aah! Aah!

00:42.869 --> 00:45.032
(GUNSHOT)

00:45.033 --> 00:46.563
AMANI: Look, you were right.

00:46.564 --> 00:48.967
I <i> was</i> in on it, only I didn't know it.

00:48.968 --> 00:50.752
I'm sorry.

00:54.932 --> 00:56.915
(GUNSHOT)

00:58.000 --> 01:04.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:17.886 --> 01:19.320
(CAR DOORS CLOSE)

01:22.258 --> 01:24.758
MAN: No luck in finding her yet.

01:27.129 --> 01:29.146
Is it possible she
doesn't wanna be found?

01:29.147 --> 01:32.014
ANN: No. She's running an errand for me.

01:32.015 --> 01:33.833
What sort of errand?

01:36.804 --> 01:38.104
Surveillance.

01:41.615 --> 01:43.599
Last call was to Amani Golkar.

01:43.600 --> 01:46.003
We tracked the GPS trail,
pinpointed where they went.

01:46.004 --> 01:48.738
I already know that. Where is she now?

01:48.739 --> 01:50.289
We're working on it.

02:29.918 --> 02:34.462
<font color="#ff0000">Sync and corrections by btsix
www.addic7ed.com</font>

02:34.816 --> 02:35.562
(GRUNTS)

02:35.563 --> 02:37.036
We have to get her to a hospital.

02:37.037 --> 02:38.885
No, she won't be safe there.

02:38.886 --> 02:41.321
We don't know who else is involved.

02:41.322 --> 02:43.022
She'll fall back into their hands.

02:43.023 --> 02:44.657
She needs a doctor.

02:44.658 --> 02:47.862
Her physical condition isn't
my concern right now.

02:47.863 --> 02:48.866
What are you saying?

02:48.867 --> 02:50.535
You wanna keep her here till
she gives up what she knows?

02:51.698 --> 02:55.335
I'm not holding her prisoner
to find out information.

02:55.336 --> 02:58.070
This poor girl is lost in the shadows,

02:58.071 --> 02:59.671
away from God's love.

02:59.672 --> 03:02.774
If we show her the light...

03:02.775 --> 03:04.109
So what's the plan?

03:04.110 --> 03:06.644
Are you praying for her to live or die?

03:06.645 --> 03:08.830
I pray for her soul.

03:11.601 --> 03:13.518
This is wrong. This is a mistake.

03:13.519 --> 03:15.086
I will not have blood on my hands.

03:15.087 --> 03:17.488
You already do.

03:17.489 --> 03:19.740
The war has started.

03:22.078 --> 03:25.462
(SPEAKING LATIN)

03:25.463 --> 03:28.665
AMANI: All right, just think
about what you're saying.

03:28.666 --> 03:30.713
We can't explain Kelly's death.

03:31.635 --> 03:33.503
The guy on the subway...

03:33.504 --> 03:35.538
surviving your attack,

03:35.539 --> 03:38.008
your suicide.

03:38.009 --> 03:41.911
So some unseen force is responsible?

03:41.912 --> 03:43.646
The massacre in Africa.

03:43.647 --> 03:46.883
The flooding in Bangladesh.

03:46.884 --> 03:50.685
I can point out the exact moment
when things got out of hand.

03:50.686 --> 03:53.088
(SIGHS) Yeah, those were disasters, man.

03:53.089 --> 03:54.856
There were other photographers there.

03:54.857 --> 03:56.992
My presence...

03:56.993 --> 03:58.627
made it tip over.

03:58.628 --> 04:00.462
Come on, dude. That's so primitive.

04:00.463 --> 04:04.099
People couldn't explain
lightning, so they blamed it

04:04.100 --> 04:07.051
on some pissed off dude on a mountain.

04:09.589 --> 04:13.641
(BOTTLE CLINKING)

04:13.642 --> 04:15.076
Look... (SIGHS)

04:15.077 --> 04:17.011
I don't have any better
explanation, all right?

04:17.012 --> 04:18.538
But I know there is one.

04:19.947 --> 04:21.798
A rational one.

04:24.703 --> 04:27.954
I'm sorry for... getting
you into this mess.

04:27.955 --> 04:30.740
(SIGHS DEEPLY) No, man. Look,
I already told you, I'm in.

04:33.845 --> 04:35.565
If you really believe this, then...

04:37.398 --> 04:39.598
I don't know. Maybe that nun can help.

04:39.599 --> 04:40.999
Simone said she could arrange a meeting.

04:41.000 --> 04:42.868
Well, that might be
another can of worms.

04:42.869 --> 04:45.171
You're thinking the Church could
be worse than Ann Rutledge?

04:45.172 --> 04:46.989
The Devil you know.

04:53.831 --> 04:55.283
That girl...

04:56.715 --> 04:58.159
Veronica, her daughter.

04:59.151 --> 05:00.918
She say anything about Rutledge?

05:00.919 --> 05:02.570
Yeah, just that, uh...

05:04.056 --> 05:06.297
She's all about the prodigal son.

05:09.030 --> 05:11.779
Seems like she blames you
for her mommy issues.

05:18.787 --> 05:23.140
(BOTTLE CLINKING)

05:23.141 --> 05:24.941
You need to go back to her.

05:25.799 --> 05:26.843
What?

05:26.844 --> 05:29.126
Get close to her again
and maybe, you know,

05:29.780 --> 05:31.780
she'll give up something
that would explain what

05:31.781 --> 05:34.049
Rutledge is up to or something
we could use as leverage.

05:34.050 --> 05:35.918
No.

05:35.919 --> 05:38.630
Man, I-I made it clear to her I
never want to see her again.

05:38.989 --> 05:39.827
She's smart.

05:39.828 --> 05:43.025
If I go back to her, she's
gonna see right through me.

05:43.026 --> 05:45.528
Rutledge and Lyons are just
the tip of this iceberg.

05:45.529 --> 05:47.496
There must be other people involved.

05:47.497 --> 05:49.531
And... and that's not
just paranoia talking.

05:49.532 --> 05:51.799
- They got money, resources.
- (SIGHS)

05:51.800 --> 05:54.136
If they truly believe they got a shot

05:54.137 --> 05:57.305
at running this whole thing
with me as a stooge,

05:57.306 --> 06:00.142
then the only chance
we got of stopping it

06:00.143 --> 06:02.210
is if we have someone on the inside.

06:02.211 --> 06:04.911
(SIGHS)

06:04.912 --> 06:07.164
I need you to do this.

06:16.090 --> 06:17.156
Yeah.

06:18.993 --> 06:20.387
Sure thing.

06:22.062 --> 06:24.730
Why would a respected psychiatrist

06:24.731 --> 06:26.982
murder someone she doesn't even know?

06:28.169 --> 06:29.835
(SIGHS)

06:29.836 --> 06:31.204
I'm not saying it was a bad shoot.

06:31.205 --> 06:32.989
Well, then why are you busting my balls?

06:38.096 --> 06:40.179
This only proves what I've
been saying all along.

06:40.180 --> 06:41.913
What's that?

06:41.914 --> 06:43.549
Damien Thorn.

06:43.550 --> 06:45.050
He's the one you should be looking at.

06:45.051 --> 06:46.918
Are you saying that Thorn is responsible

06:46.919 --> 06:49.721
- for everything that happened here?
- Why was his shrink here?

06:49.722 --> 06:51.623
There was no official request
for her to come down here

06:51.624 --> 06:53.292
and visit Powell.

06:53.293 --> 06:56.660
Someone sent Dr. Matthews,
someone who wanted Powell dead.

06:56.661 --> 07:00.231
Weird shit happens around
this jerkoff all the time.

07:00.232 --> 07:01.832
Freaky deaths.

07:01.833 --> 07:03.201
There's a-a... this darkness

07:03.202 --> 07:04.668
that just doesn't make any sense.

07:04.669 --> 07:06.170
Told you to drop it.

07:06.171 --> 07:08.138
Okay, look, just run it down for me.

07:08.139 --> 07:10.674
You show up in a trailer
in the middle of nowhere

07:10.675 --> 07:14.177
to find Powell conveniently
beaten to a pulp.

07:14.178 --> 07:15.878
No.

07:15.879 --> 07:17.280
He was like that when I arrived.

07:17.281 --> 07:19.249
He claimed the Devil did it.

07:19.250 --> 07:21.684
Powell was a deranged psychopath, right?

07:21.685 --> 07:23.286
He and Thorn, they go way back.

07:23.287 --> 07:24.987
He knew shit about Thorn,

07:24.988 --> 07:27.657
so Thorn sent his shrink
down here to take him out.

07:27.658 --> 07:29.891
That's... that... That's how he does it.

07:29.892 --> 07:31.227
No fingerprints.

07:31.228 --> 07:34.763
He, uh, threatened my...
my family, my son.

07:34.764 --> 07:36.998
He set my car on fire.

07:36.999 --> 07:38.834
He had a dog attack me
right here in the station.

07:38.835 --> 07:40.702
Okay.

07:40.703 --> 07:43.339
Okay, look, we can't trust you out there

07:43.340 --> 07:46.007
with a... with a gun and a badge, okay?

07:46.008 --> 07:47.392
I want 'em.

07:50.763 --> 07:52.247
(SCOFFS)

07:52.248 --> 07:54.081
All right. Sure.

07:54.082 --> 07:55.783
(GUN THUDS) Cover your own ass.

07:55.784 --> 07:57.352
- (BADGE THUDS)
- Oh, come on, you know,

07:57.353 --> 07:59.720
don't make this any worse
than it has to be.

07:59.721 --> 08:00.888
(DOOR SLAMS)

08:00.889 --> 08:02.257
(GRETA SPEAKING LATIN)

08:02.258 --> 08:04.824
VERONICA: (WEAKLY)
I hope you rot in hell.

08:04.825 --> 08:08.962
I'm not the one trying to bring
about the end of the world.

08:08.963 --> 08:12.015
Who knows if that's even true.

08:15.861 --> 08:17.377
(SPEAKING LATIN)

08:17.378 --> 08:18.815
All my life,

08:18.816 --> 08:22.587
Mother fawned over her precious Damien.

08:23.009 --> 08:26.745
She never even met him
until a few weeks ago.

08:26.746 --> 08:28.281
And yet she's devoted
her whole life to him,

08:28.282 --> 08:29.782
destroying everything.

08:29.783 --> 08:33.836
Faith drives us to do evil things.

08:35.273 --> 08:38.390
Did she have anything to
do with my sister's death?

08:38.390 --> 08:41.243
That was a greater power.
(INHALES SHARPLY)

08:49.052 --> 08:52.019
(RESUMES SPEAKING LATIN)

08:54.490 --> 08:56.072
- Listen to me.
- (GRUNTS)

08:56.073 --> 08:58.709
(WHISPERING) You're bleeding out.
I'll help you.

08:58.710 --> 09:00.544
Tell me how to stop this...
Your mom, Damien.

09:00.545 --> 09:02.713
- Just tell me how...
- You can't.

09:02.714 --> 09:05.699
(LABORED BREATHING)

09:08.371 --> 09:10.187
Goddamnit.

09:10.188 --> 09:11.754
She's not giving us anything!
She's dying!

09:11.755 --> 09:13.823
You're supposed to be compassionate.

09:13.824 --> 09:15.991
This is cruel. I know this is right.

09:15.992 --> 09:17.593
She knows.

09:18.862 --> 09:21.297
She knows you brought
the Church into this.

09:21.298 --> 09:22.798
<i>She</i> found <i> me.</i>

09:22.799 --> 09:24.066
Doesn't matter.

09:24.067 --> 09:27.983
Only way you can save yourself now

09:28.938 --> 09:31.105
is to turn me over.

09:31.106 --> 09:33.775
You can still walk away.

09:33.776 --> 09:37.078
All she cares about is getting me back.

09:37.079 --> 09:41.900
Killing you isn't worth her time.
(INHALES SHARPLY)

09:45.238 --> 09:48.138
What does Ann Rutledge want from Damien?

09:49.324 --> 09:51.225
Why is she after him?

09:51.226 --> 09:54.328
I know she sent men into
his apartment to kill him.

09:56.163 --> 09:58.245
(EXHALES DEEPLY) That wasn't a hit.

09:58.867 --> 10:01.869
They were there to teach him a lesson.

10:01.870 --> 10:02.960
Bullshit.

10:02.961 --> 10:05.418
My mother doesn't like to be ignored.

10:05.419 --> 10:08.841
And she sure as hell
doesn't like for people

10:08.842 --> 10:10.218
to take what's hers.

10:10.219 --> 10:13.754
And if she had you back,
what would your mother do?

10:13.755 --> 10:15.657
Hmm?

10:15.658 --> 10:18.375
Send you back as an assassin.

10:19.761 --> 10:22.863
She has you in service to the enemy,

10:22.864 --> 10:25.181
Satan himself.

10:26.235 --> 10:27.899
A mother...

10:29.605 --> 10:31.872
protects.

10:31.873 --> 10:34.542
She loves her children.

10:34.543 --> 10:37.151
Her love <i> is</i> God's love.

10:39.831 --> 10:41.544
Your mother...

10:42.650 --> 10:45.519
put a gun in your hand

10:45.520 --> 10:48.838
and darkness in your heart.

10:54.345 --> 10:57.146
Is that a mother's love?

11:02.787 --> 11:05.688
You don't know shit about me.

11:08.025 --> 11:09.575
(SIGHS)

11:09.576 --> 11:13.211
(INHALES AND EXHALES SHARPLY)

11:13.212 --> 11:15.713
We must pray.

11:15.714 --> 11:18.683
(GROANS) Don't touch me.

11:18.684 --> 11:20.018
- (LAUGHING)
- Enough!

11:20.019 --> 11:22.670
- (GASPS)
- Enough!

11:24.241 --> 11:26.057
(EXHALES)

11:26.058 --> 11:29.042
(BREATHING RAGGEDLY)

11:32.195 --> 11:33.743
(POUNDING ON DOOR)

11:34.845 --> 11:37.847
(LOCK CLANKS)

11:38.458 --> 11:41.294
- (DOOR CREAKS)
- Damien Thorn?

11:41.295 --> 11:44.614
Lieutenant Murnau, NYPD.

11:45.186 --> 11:48.655
Uh, I was just on my way out.
Uh, what's the problem?

11:48.656 --> 11:52.860
Well... I prefer we talk inside.

11:55.030 --> 11:56.997
(DOOR CREAKS CLOSED)

11:56.998 --> 11:58.181
(LOCK CLANKS)

11:58.182 --> 11:59.733
What's this about?

11:59.734 --> 12:01.735
Detective Shay.

12:03.405 --> 12:07.741
Shay, uh, was involved in a
shooting down at the precinct.

12:07.742 --> 12:11.010
He had to use deadly force
against Dr. Matthews.

12:11.011 --> 12:13.195
She was stabbing a murder suspect

12:13.196 --> 12:14.647
when Shay intervened.

12:14.648 --> 12:16.616
She killed Charles Powell?

12:19.253 --> 12:20.887
How did you know that?

12:22.691 --> 12:26.108
I, uh, I heard about Cray Marquand

12:26.109 --> 12:27.809
and... and Powell's arrest...

12:27.810 --> 12:30.407
Did you ever mention Powell to Matthews?

12:31.927 --> 12:33.081
No.

12:33.082 --> 12:34.101
Huh.

12:35.034 --> 12:37.000
We can't seem to find any connection.

12:38.922 --> 12:41.339
We searched her office
for motive, and...

12:42.810 --> 12:45.175
couldn't find any notes on you.

12:50.249 --> 12:53.150
She was your shrink, right?

12:55.822 --> 12:57.404
Yeah, she was.

12:57.405 --> 12:58.403
Hmm.

12:59.374 --> 13:02.141
Shay's recent behavior
has complicated things.

13:02.908 --> 13:05.900
He's been relieved of duty,
pending a full investigation.

13:05.901 --> 13:08.386
Now if you want to file for
a restraining order...

13:08.387 --> 13:10.222
You think there's a need for that?

13:12.226 --> 13:13.253
Well...

13:14.069 --> 13:16.451
I don't wanna talk bad
about another cop,

13:17.613 --> 13:19.523
but once a guy breaks...

13:21.016 --> 13:22.099
you never know.

13:26.705 --> 13:27.999
I'll think about it.

13:29.290 --> 13:32.848
Uh, thanks for coming by, Lieutenant.

13:34.578 --> 13:35.731
Of course.

13:36.413 --> 13:39.415
(LOCK CLICKS, DOOR CREAKS)

13:44.422 --> 13:46.572
(DOOR CREAKS)

13:46.573 --> 13:48.574
(LOCK CLICKS)

13:57.839 --> 13:59.695
(PHONE BEEPS, LINE RINGING)

13:59.696 --> 14:01.114
(CELL PHONE VIBRATES, BEEPS)

14:01.115 --> 14:02.045
SIMONE: Hello?

14:02.046 --> 14:04.072
Amani told me you met a
woman from the Church.

14:04.073 --> 14:05.114
I wanna meet her.

14:06.692 --> 14:09.177
I don't think that's a very good idea.

14:14.037 --> 14:16.270
I have nowhere else to go.

14:18.554 --> 14:20.404
(SIGHS)

14:20.405 --> 14:21.777
Okay.

14:23.041 --> 14:24.417
I'll send you the address.

14:37.139 --> 14:38.371
(ENGINE TURNS OFF)

14:43.410 --> 14:45.577
(GRAVEL CRUNCHING)

15:16.142 --> 15:17.507
Damien.

15:30.222 --> 15:34.020
I am Greta Fraueva of Scisco Dei.

15:34.021 --> 15:36.870
She investigates things for the Vatican.

15:36.871 --> 15:39.833
You bear the mark of the Beast?

15:42.037 --> 15:43.837
Show it to me?

15:54.716 --> 15:56.348
(ANIMAL CRIES IN DISTANCE)

16:09.062 --> 16:11.129
(WHISPERS) Oh, you poor man.

16:14.334 --> 16:17.752
(SNIFFLING AND CRYING)

16:17.753 --> 16:19.136
(INHALES DEEPLY)

16:19.137 --> 16:22.757
Do not believe them,
that you are the Devil,

16:22.758 --> 16:24.959
Son of Satan, Son of Night.

16:24.960 --> 16:26.393
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

16:26.394 --> 16:30.414
You are God's child.

16:34.153 --> 16:35.970
You're the only one who says that.

16:35.971 --> 16:37.320
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

16:39.191 --> 16:43.009
We are all part of the Divine Plan.

16:43.010 --> 16:44.894
Job suffered

16:44.895 --> 16:46.846
and he never lost his faith.

16:46.847 --> 16:49.198
I'm not a man of faith.
I just believe what I see.

16:51.002 --> 16:53.269
And what have you seen?

16:56.207 --> 16:58.115
Something, uh...

17:00.159 --> 17:02.010
Spirits, maybe?

17:05.571 --> 17:07.617
I was at, uh, the VA hospital and...

17:09.364 --> 17:11.069
I saw seven soldiers.

17:11.069 --> 17:13.805
They were each wounded.

17:14.603 --> 17:17.942
And they, uh, they spoke in unison,

17:17.943 --> 17:20.511
but like it was coming from one mind.

17:20.512 --> 17:22.842
And what did this voice say?

17:24.957 --> 17:27.351
It quoted from the Bible.
Stuff about the Beast.

17:27.352 --> 17:30.354
- (GRETA INHALES SHARPLY)
- Hell followed behind me.

17:30.355 --> 17:31.989
(SIGHS) So it's the...

17:31.990 --> 17:34.457
The 7-headed dragon from
the book of <i> Revelation.</i>

17:34.458 --> 17:36.059
This... this appeared to you?

17:36.060 --> 17:38.044
Yeah. I-I don't think
it was the first time.

17:46.521 --> 17:51.873
When Kelly died, she said
something, uh, grabbed her.

17:52.722 --> 17:54.209
It pulled her under.

17:54.536 --> 17:55.803
No.

17:58.032 --> 17:59.347
(INHALES DEEPLY)

17:59.348 --> 18:02.284
(ANIMAL CRIES IN DISTANCE)

18:02.285 --> 18:04.136
(WHISPERS) Her face...

18:06.240 --> 18:08.339
There was something down there with her?

18:10.543 --> 18:12.927
(ANIMAL CRIES IN DISTANCE)

18:12.928 --> 18:14.979
I think something very
real is following me.

18:18.351 --> 18:19.917
Can you help?

18:22.155 --> 18:24.955
That's why I'm here.

18:27.592 --> 18:30.911
(GRETA SNIFFLES)

18:30.912 --> 18:33.159
Hey, Veronica, it's me.

18:33.848 --> 18:35.015
(CAR CHIRPS)

18:35.016 --> 18:38.284
Listen, um... can we talk?

18:38.285 --> 18:40.153
- I just, uh...
- (ENGINE STARTS)

18:40.154 --> 18:42.521
- really hate the way we left things.
- (ENGINE REVS)

18:42.522 --> 18:44.840
- Yeah.
- (TIRES SQUEAL)

18:47.912 --> 18:49.228
Hey! (GROANS)

18:49.229 --> 18:52.546
Aah! (GRUNTING)

18:54.134 --> 18:56.251
(CAR DOOR CLOSES)

18:56.252 --> 18:57.986
(TIRES SCREECH)

19:00.805 --> 19:04.307
(INSECTS CHIRPING)

19:06.945 --> 19:09.312
He's safe with me. You can go.

19:11.398 --> 19:13.531
Rutledge's daughter is here.

19:13.532 --> 19:16.333
She's dying.

19:16.334 --> 19:18.569
If Rutledge knows she's here,
she will come for her.

19:21.107 --> 19:24.675
He's right. You should go tend to her.

19:30.181 --> 19:31.581
I have him.

19:34.920 --> 19:36.386
Come.

19:39.024 --> 19:40.590
Come.

19:57.628 --> 19:59.628
(DOOR OPENS)

20:04.681 --> 20:06.163
(DOOR CREAKS AND CLOSES)

20:06.164 --> 20:07.606
(WHISPERS) Listen,

20:07.607 --> 20:09.650
I'm gonna get you out of here.

20:09.651 --> 20:12.420
(LOCK CLICKS)

20:14.057 --> 20:15.973
- (DOOR RATTLES)
- Hey!

20:15.974 --> 20:17.909
Hey! Open this door!

20:17.910 --> 20:21.528
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

20:51.726 --> 20:53.125
Where is she?

20:54.476 --> 20:55.761
Who?

20:56.512 --> 20:57.914
Veronica.

20:58.964 --> 21:00.639
Spying on someone?

21:01.016 --> 21:02.700
I'm sure you have a lot of enemies.

21:02.701 --> 21:04.602
You've already started
off on the wrong foot.

21:04.603 --> 21:06.154
Don't make it worse.

21:06.155 --> 21:08.439
Hey, don't threaten me, all right?

21:08.440 --> 21:10.390
I've dealt with a lot
scarier assholes than you.

21:10.391 --> 21:11.287
(CHUCKLES)

21:11.288 --> 21:12.857
And aren't you forgetting something?

21:12.858 --> 21:15.305
Damien and I go way back.

21:16.300 --> 21:17.759
We're friends.

21:18.413 --> 21:19.994
Even you can't mess with that.

21:21.621 --> 21:23.204
You're a small man

21:24.146 --> 21:26.134
who took a wrong turn in a theater

21:26.135 --> 21:29.159
and somehow wandered onto the stage.

21:30.615 --> 21:33.257
Don't dare think yourself a player.

21:36.195 --> 21:37.712
Now...

21:39.747 --> 21:41.365
Where's my daughter?

21:43.801 --> 21:46.168
I honestly have no idea.

21:49.756 --> 21:51.898
Who's this nun from the Vatican?

21:53.530 --> 21:54.977
I don't know who you're talking about.

21:54.978 --> 21:57.797
She's here to kill Damien.
Why else would they send her?

21:58.756 --> 22:00.249
Like I said,

22:00.250 --> 22:02.334
- I can't help you.
- (CHUCKLES)

22:02.335 --> 22:04.452
I can see why he keeps you around.

22:04.453 --> 22:07.439
Yeah, he wasn't too happy you
sent Veronica after him.

22:07.440 --> 22:09.991
When he finds out you kidnapped me,

22:10.802 --> 22:11.826
well, he just might kill you.

22:11.827 --> 22:13.361
Oh, he's already had that chance.

22:13.362 --> 22:14.945
It's not in him.

22:16.149 --> 22:17.175
Yet.

22:19.055 --> 22:20.884
Don't think you're
safe from him, either.

22:20.885 --> 22:22.219
You don't know who he is.

22:22.220 --> 22:25.889
I know <i> exactly</i> who he is.

22:25.890 --> 22:29.743
This nun's here to kill him.
She may have killed Veronica.

22:29.744 --> 22:32.746
I understand if you don't
wanna help me. Fine.

22:32.747 --> 22:35.898
But the only way you can save Damien

22:35.899 --> 22:38.418
is to tell me where this nun is.

22:43.792 --> 22:46.075
I'll find her anyway.

22:46.076 --> 22:49.296
It's just a question if I
do before she kills them.

22:51.399 --> 22:53.449
All right, fine.

22:53.450 --> 22:54.966
I'll take you to him.

22:58.071 --> 23:00.088
You really think you can stop

23:00.089 --> 23:02.941
whatever's causing these
deaths around me?

23:05.813 --> 23:10.130
I've dealt with things like this before,

23:10.131 --> 23:14.084
but never this severe.

23:16.923 --> 23:18.823
What if I really am the Antichrist?

23:20.092 --> 23:22.532
Then that...

23:23.512 --> 23:25.312
is God's will.

23:25.313 --> 23:29.866
- And nothing can be done?
- You must have faith.

23:29.867 --> 23:32.235
God has a plan for all of us.

23:32.236 --> 23:35.789
If yours is to bring about the
Second Coming of Christ...

23:35.790 --> 23:37.557
Then God can do His own dirty work.

23:37.558 --> 23:39.125
(INHALES DEEPLY)

23:39.126 --> 23:42.054
You may have been chosen.

23:44.187 --> 23:48.250
You... you make that sound
like it's a good thing.

23:49.171 --> 23:50.803
This feels like a terminal illness.

23:50.804 --> 23:53.439
My... my life results
in countless deaths.

23:53.440 --> 23:58.126
How can you devote your
life to a God like that?

23:59.929 --> 24:02.129
(WHISPERS) Do not tempt me.

24:12.208 --> 24:14.526
Don't look at me like that.

24:14.527 --> 24:16.277
I'm just as lost as you are.

24:16.278 --> 24:20.705
If there is a demon within
you, then it will not let go.

24:21.533 --> 24:25.318
We have to break its grasp.

24:27.590 --> 24:30.474
(GROANS AND GASPS)

24:30.475 --> 24:34.026
(PANTING)

24:51.855 --> 24:53.280
(DAMIEN GROANS)

24:56.080 --> 24:59.048
(VINES STRETCHING)

25:04.222 --> 25:07.539
(GRUNTING)

25:08.187 --> 25:09.521
(YELLS)

25:09.522 --> 25:12.508
(GASPING AND GROANING)

25:16.781 --> 25:19.748
(GASPING)

25:22.252 --> 25:24.252
(GROANS)

25:26.390 --> 25:27.739
Mom.

25:27.740 --> 25:30.158
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

25:32.429 --> 25:34.229
Veronica.

25:34.230 --> 25:36.714
- Mom.
- (WHISPERS) Do you hear me?

25:36.715 --> 25:38.400
Where are you?

25:38.401 --> 25:41.718
(GROANS) Mom... I...

25:41.719 --> 25:43.554
Shh, shh. shh.

25:43.555 --> 25:45.222
(INHALES SHARPLY)

25:45.223 --> 25:48.775
(HOWLING IN DISTANCE)

25:55.267 --> 25:58.284
(HOWLING CONTINUES)

26:04.792 --> 26:08.728
(DOOR RATTLING)

26:40.393 --> 26:41.763
James...

26:42.360 --> 26:43.767
what are you doing?

26:44.413 --> 26:46.214
I'm building a case. It's all here.

26:46.215 --> 26:47.547
- Stop.
- Proof.

26:47.548 --> 26:49.832
- Stop.
- We're in danger, Patrick.

26:49.833 --> 26:52.452
I was mauled by a dog.
Jacob almost died.

26:52.453 --> 26:53.987
I barely escaped being burned to death.

26:53.988 --> 26:56.272
Those were accidents.
Those were not accidents!

26:56.273 --> 26:58.725
None of these were accidents.

26:58.726 --> 27:00.910
Something horrible is
going on out there.

27:00.911 --> 27:02.378
And... and everyone's just

27:02.379 --> 27:03.830
burying their goddamn heads in the sand.

27:03.831 --> 27:05.631
He's gotta be stopped.

27:05.632 --> 27:07.216
Honey, you're losing it.

27:10.535 --> 27:13.686
Daddy, are the monsters coming back?

27:13.687 --> 27:15.480
Hey, go to your room, buddy.
Everything's okay.

27:15.481 --> 27:17.634
No, no, no, Jacob, come here.
Come here, come here.

27:17.635 --> 27:19.902
Listen. Listen to me. (PANTING)

27:19.903 --> 27:21.953
Everything is not okay.

27:21.954 --> 27:23.672
There <i> are</i> monsters,

27:23.673 --> 27:25.941
- but I'm gonna protect you from them.
- Hey, hey.

27:25.942 --> 27:27.859
He almost died. He needs to know why.

27:27.860 --> 27:30.896
We're going to my brother's house.
Come on. Come on.

27:33.534 --> 27:35.133
(WHISPERS) The Devil did it.

27:35.134 --> 27:37.486
What? (GASPS)

27:37.487 --> 27:39.870
Hey. Hey, come on.

27:42.509 --> 27:44.058
(DOOR OPENS)

27:44.059 --> 27:45.543
(DOOR CLOSES)

27:53.886 --> 27:56.886
(ENGINE STARTS)

27:56.887 --> 27:58.739
- (VEHICLE DEPARTS)
- Patrick!

27:58.740 --> 28:00.707
Jacob!

28:00.708 --> 28:04.761
(DOG SNARLING AND BARKING)

28:14.572 --> 28:16.071
Aah!

28:16.072 --> 28:17.623
(PANTING)

28:17.624 --> 28:20.238
VERONICA: Aah!

28:20.729 --> 28:23.696
(SCREAMING)

28:23.697 --> 28:24.963
Please!

28:24.964 --> 28:27.065
Please!

28:27.066 --> 28:29.550
Somebody help me!

28:29.551 --> 28:31.018
(CRYING)

28:33.490 --> 28:35.507
(CRUCIFIX THUDS)

28:35.508 --> 28:37.759
(VERONICA BREATHING HEAVILY)

28:39.863 --> 28:41.228
(GROANS)

28:41.229 --> 28:43.581
- Come on.
- (GROANS)

28:43.582 --> 28:45.483
Come on. Come on.

28:45.484 --> 28:46.950
Come on.

28:46.951 --> 28:50.587
(WHISPERS) Okay. Okay.

28:50.588 --> 28:52.589
- (GROANS)
- Come on.

28:59.782 --> 29:02.599
(WHISPERS) Stop.

29:02.600 --> 29:03.983
Stop.

29:07.021 --> 29:08.888
(GRUNTS)

29:13.294 --> 29:17.680
(SPEAKING LATIN)

29:17.681 --> 29:21.666
(GROANING)

29:29.576 --> 29:33.211
(GASPING)

29:42.121 --> 29:44.855
(COUGHS AND GASPS)

29:54.699 --> 29:58.651
(PANTING) Please. Please, stop.

29:58.652 --> 30:00.553
(GASPING)

30:00.554 --> 30:02.138
(GRUNTS)

30:04.409 --> 30:06.242
(KISSES)

30:07.879 --> 30:10.062
(WEAKLY) Please, stop.

30:10.063 --> 30:12.380
Stop. (GRUNTS)

30:41.028 --> 30:43.411
- (WHISPERS) Okay.
- (VERONICA GROANING)

30:43.412 --> 30:46.847
(GASPS AND GRUNTS)

30:46.848 --> 30:48.849
- Okay.
- (INHALES SHARPLY)

30:48.850 --> 30:52.536
- Okay. Come on. Come on.
- (GROANS)

30:55.327 --> 30:59.061
(GRETA SPEAKING LATIN)

31:18.481 --> 31:19.764
Hey.

31:19.765 --> 31:23.234
(CONTINUES SPEAKING LATIN)

31:23.235 --> 31:26.571
If I die, this... This
passes on to another.

31:26.572 --> 31:28.639
Even with all my experience,

31:28.640 --> 31:31.842
I don't claim to understand
the workings of spirits.

31:31.843 --> 31:34.211
Put your faith in Christ.

31:34.212 --> 31:35.779
It is time.

31:35.780 --> 31:39.082
- You must be reborn. The demon...
- Don't do this.

31:39.083 --> 31:41.284
- Must be in the Earth, closer to Hell.
- Hey, no, no! No! No!

31:41.285 --> 31:44.153
- No! Hey, hey, hey, please. Let go!
- When you arise, you can be reborn!

31:44.154 --> 31:45.655
- Pull me back up now! No!
- It will fall away!

31:45.656 --> 31:48.458
- Christ promises the Resurrection!
- No, no! No!

31:48.459 --> 31:49.793
You will be saved.

31:49.794 --> 31:51.694
(SCREAMING)

31:51.695 --> 31:54.780
(LABORED BREATHING)

31:56.584 --> 31:58.233
(DAMIEN SCREAMING IN DISTANCE)

31:58.234 --> 32:00.469
Okay. Okay, come on. Over here.

32:00.470 --> 32:03.456
(GRUNTS AND GROANS)

32:05.860 --> 32:09.778
Okay. Listen to me, look...
you're gonna be okay.

32:09.779 --> 32:11.212
Stay here, okay?

32:11.213 --> 32:13.815
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

32:13.816 --> 32:16.267
(DAMIEN SCREAMS)

32:21.808 --> 32:25.192
(SCREAMING)

32:25.193 --> 32:27.394
Christ promises the Resurrection.

32:27.395 --> 32:29.951
You will be saved.

32:31.851 --> 32:34.063
(PANTING)

32:34.559 --> 32:39.773
(SPEAKING LATIN)

32:39.774 --> 32:41.575
(SCREAMS)

32:41.576 --> 32:42.825
Hey!

32:45.536 --> 32:48.121
(CONTINUES SPEAKING LATIN)

32:48.549 --> 32:50.950
- Amen.
- ALL: Amen.

32:50.951 --> 32:55.095
(GRETA SPEAKING LATIN)

32:55.807 --> 32:59.791
(VOICE ECHOING)

32:59.792 --> 33:03.545
(SCREAMING)

33:05.549 --> 33:07.766
<i>(KELLY SCREAMS)</i>

33:07.767 --> 33:10.902
<i>(CREATURE GROWLS AND HISSES)</i>

33:10.903 --> 33:13.404
<i>(SNARLING)</i>

33:13.405 --> 33:15.674
(GASPS) Aah!

33:15.675 --> 33:20.394
<i>(HISSING)</i>

33:22.665 --> 33:24.748
Hey!

33:24.749 --> 33:28.569
<i>(GROWLING AND SNARLING)</i>

33:31.974 --> 33:34.290
- (SCREAMING)
- (SHRIEKS)

33:34.291 --> 33:39.261
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

33:39.262 --> 33:43.600
(INSECTS CHIRPING)

33:43.601 --> 33:45.568
(INHALES SHARPLY)

33:45.569 --> 33:49.388
(VARIOUS ANIMAL SOUNDS)

33:52.025 --> 33:56.612
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

33:56.613 --> 34:00.466
(DOGS HOWLING IN DISTANCE)

34:09.775 --> 34:13.543
(VARIOUS ANIMAL SOUNDS)

34:15.782 --> 34:17.380
(GRUNTS)

34:27.893 --> 34:29.324
Aah!

34:31.730 --> 34:35.849
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

34:35.850 --> 34:37.717
Aah!

34:37.717 --> 34:40.453
(SCREAMING)

34:40.454 --> 34:43.505
(GASPING)

34:45.576 --> 34:47.726
Aah!

34:47.726 --> 34:51.346
(SCREAMING)

35:02.826 --> 35:06.460
(GAGGING)

35:16.489 --> 35:20.258
(BRANCHES CRUNCHING)

35:51.622 --> 35:53.739
(GASPS)

35:53.740 --> 35:58.293
(CRYING)

36:07.304 --> 36:10.305
(LATCH CLANKS, DOOR CREAKS)

36:28.691 --> 36:30.824
<i>(CHILD GIGGLES)</i>

36:40.301 --> 36:41.701
(SWITCH CLICKS)

36:54.247 --> 36:55.513
(SWITCH CLICKS)

37:12.965 --> 37:16.450
(JACOB'S VOICE, WARPED)
<i>Daddy, help me. Daddy.</i>

37:16.451 --> 37:18.001
- Jacob?
- (DOOR CREAKING)

37:21.440 --> 37:23.689
<i>Daddy, help me. They're hurting me.</i>

37:23.690 --> 37:27.326
Who? Who's hurting you?
Are you here, Jacob?

37:27.327 --> 37:29.962
<i>Daddy.</i>

37:29.963 --> 37:31.798
Jacob?

37:31.799 --> 37:33.933
<i>(INDISTINCT WHISPER AND GROWL)</i>

37:33.934 --> 37:36.536
<i>Daddy, help me.</i>

37:36.537 --> 37:37.870
Jacob?

37:37.871 --> 37:39.371
<i>(INDISTINCT WHISPER)</i>

37:39.372 --> 37:42.924
<i>(GROWLING)</i>

37:44.561 --> 37:47.479
<i>(INDISTINCT WHISPERING)</i>

37:47.480 --> 37:48.913
<i>(GROWLING)</i>

37:48.914 --> 37:51.817
<i>Daddy. Daddy.</i>

37:51.818 --> 37:53.485
<i>(WHISPERING CONTINUES)</i>

37:53.486 --> 37:55.904
<i>(LOUD GROWL)</i>

38:00.009 --> 38:05.028
<i>(GROWLING)</i>

38:05.029 --> 38:07.314
<i>Daddy, help me.</i>

38:12.822 --> 38:14.904
Aah!

38:14.905 --> 38:18.758
<i>(EVIL LAUGHTER)</i>

38:24.032 --> 38:26.949
<i>(GROWLING)</i>

38:26.950 --> 38:28.951
(SCREAMING)

38:28.952 --> 38:30.587
No, no!

38:30.588 --> 38:34.406
(NUNS CHANTING IN LATIN)

38:37.545 --> 38:41.697
<i>(GROWLING)</i>

38:41.698 --> 38:45.801
<i>(WARPED VOICES)
Son of Night, your name is death,</i>

38:45.802 --> 38:47.636
<i>And Hell will... (SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY)</i>

38:47.637 --> 38:49.470
<i>(WARPED SCREAMS)</i>

38:49.471 --> 38:54.375
(SCREAMING)

38:54.376 --> 38:55.843
ANN'S VOICE: <i>The Power
wants what it wants.</i>

38:55.844 --> 38:59.497
<i>Your spirit and life
will cease to exist.</i>

39:01.367 --> 39:02.767
MAN'S WARPED VOICE: <i>The Beast...</i>

39:05.871 --> 39:09.639
(SCREAMING)

39:11.042 --> 39:12.859
(NUNS CONTINUE CHANTING IN LATIN)

39:12.860 --> 39:14.895
SIMONE: Damien!

39:14.896 --> 39:16.429
Stop!

39:16.430 --> 39:18.398
What have you done?

39:18.399 --> 39:21.701
GRETA: This is God's work.
Do not interfere!

39:21.702 --> 39:26.388
<i>(GROWLING)</i>

39:29.994 --> 39:33.729
(SCREAMING)

39:55.685 --> 39:59.419
(DOGS HOWLING IN DISTANCE)

40:05.476 --> 40:06.727
(HEAD LAMP CLATTERS)

40:10.766 --> 40:12.599
(BLADE ZINGS)

40:22.425 --> 40:28.698
(SPEAKING LATIN)

40:28.699 --> 40:30.715
(GRUNTS) Aah!

40:32.653 --> 40:36.771
(ANIMAL HOWLS IN DISTANCE)

40:36.772 --> 40:40.208
(PANTING)

40:40.209 --> 40:42.060
- (SQUISH)
- (GROANS)

40:48.883 --> 40:52.586
(GROANING AND GASPING)

40:52.587 --> 40:55.606
Uhh! (PANTING)

41:06.900 --> 41:09.535
(CONTINUES GASPING)

41:20.498 --> 41:24.049
(LABORED BREATHING)

